text: Robert Stevenson (born 7 December 1968) is a Canadian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Fredericton
